Initial commit: BitTON.AI frontend with wallet-based auth

- Next.js 14 + TypeScript + Tailwind + wagmi v2 + RainbowKit
- Wallet signature required for registration and login
- Registration: email + password + wallet sign + sponsor code (from ?ref= param)
- Login: wallet connect + challenge-sign flow
- Email verification page (/verify-email?token=)
- AuthContext with JWT access/refresh token management
- ProtectedRoute guard + conditional LayoutShell
- Full staking platform UI: dashboard, vault, staking, rewards, vesting, withdraw, referrals, history, admin
- All contract ABIs and hooks for on-chain interactions
- Static export for Netlify deployment

